    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it remains very reliable; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts exactly as it should without hesitation. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use consistent with its age, the interior has been kept clean and comfortable. All major systems are fully functional, making this a dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
