    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in an impeccable state that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This specimen exhibits a flawless aesthetic profile, characterized by a factory-perfect exterior and an interior that retains its original luster and tactile integrity. Rigorously vetted for mechanical excellence, this automobile offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its debut. For the discerning individual seeking a peerless acquisition, this offering represents the definitive standard in automotive maintenance and presentation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
